      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>grated ginger</strong>, <strong>white</strong> <strong>miso paste</strong>,<strong> toasted sesame oil</strong> and <strong>agave</strong> with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>in a small bowl</p><p>Stir it all together – this is your <strong>miso dressing</strong></p>",
