      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>tamari mushrooms & roasted broccoli</strong> over the <strong>quinoa </strong>and drizzle the<strong> miso dressing </strong>all over</p><p>Drain the <strong>quick-pickled carrot ribbons</strong> and serve them to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chilli rounds</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>toasted sesame seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
